text: WEATHER EXTRA: One more day of gloomy weather Published: Dec. 29, 2023 at 8:09 AM EST|Updated: 47 minutes ago LANSING, Mich. (WILX) - We round out the last week of 2023 with another day of gloomy weather. First Alert Meteorologist Colton Cichoracki joins the News 10+ Digital Desk with a look at your forecast for the last few days of the year.
